item.title: Terror Alert: Washington State
item.description: I got this link on GatewayPundit: The FBI is asking for the public’s help to identify two men who have been seen acting strangely aboard Washington State ferries recently. According to federal agents, passengers have seen the men on several occasions exhibiting unusual behavior. The FBI did not say precisely what that unusual The Submarine Base at Bremerton is home to the Navy’s Pacific fleet of Trident class submarines.
